accessibility.text: Font data is compressed. Sites using WOFF will use less bandwidth and will load faster than if they used equivalent uncompressed TrueType or OpenType files.
Font data is compressed. Sites using WOFF will use less bandwidth and will load faster than if they used equivalent uncompressed TrueType or OpenType files.
Many font vendors that are unwilling to license their TrueType or OpenType format fonts for use on the web will license WOFFformat fonts.
